This project presents an interactive Mobile Sales Analysis Dashboard built in Power BI, designed to analyze sales-related metrics for various smartphone models in 2025.
The dashboard transforms raw data (Product Name, Price, Rating, Review Count) into meaningful insights using multiple visualizations.

